filing unfair labor practice charges with the National Labor Relations Board. 
</P>
<P>
 The former head of the soccer team of Bastia, Corsica, where temporary seating 
collapsed before a game two years ago killing 15 people and injuring more than 
2,000, was shot and killed outside his home, police said. 
