 The Raiders will play the Dallas Cowboys, Pittsburgh Steelers, Philadelphia 
Eagles and Indianapolis Colts at the Coliseum next season in addition to their 
four AFC West rivals, according to the preliminary schedule announced by the 
NFL on Monday. 
</P>
<P>
