New York Jets, New York Giants and Washington Redskins. 
</P>
<P>
 The Rams will play home-and-away games with the Carolina Panthers and their 
three longtime NFC West rivals, and face the Miami Dolphins, Buffalo Bills, 
Chicago Bears and Washington Redskins at home -- wherever that may be. 
</P>
<P>
 Ram non-divisional road games will be against the Eagles, Jets, Colts and 
Green Bay Packers. 
