REGIONAL ROUNDUP: HARMONY CHAIRMAN BUYS 950,000 SHARES OF STOCK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Harmony Holdings Inc., a Burbank-based producer of special-effect television 
commercials and music videos, said the company's chairman, Harvey Bibicoff, has 
