</P>
<P>
 Sunday, 11 a.m. to 2 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 No charge for food court and souvenir boutique. Float viewing is $1 per person 
for one location, $2 per person for two or more locations. Children under 8 are 
free. 
</P>
<P>
 * Rose Bowl stadium viewing 
</P>
<P>
 Enter Gate A 
</P>
<P>
 Today through Sunday 
</P>
<P>
 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. $2 per person 
</P>
<P>
 * Band performances 
</P>
<P>
 Rose Bowl Parking Area K 
</P>
<P>
 Thursday and Friday: Indonesian dancers, 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Saturday: Indonesian dancers, 11 a.m. to noon; Indonesian band, noon to 1 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Sunday: Meijo Gakuin High School Band, Japan, noon to 1 p.m; Pasadena City 
College Band, 1:45 to 2:15 p.m. No charge. 
</P>
<P>
 * $100,000 hole-in-one golf shootout 
</P>
<P>
