<DOCNO> LA122794-0159 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 111822 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 27, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
