<TEXT>
<P>
 Still playing -- A story in Saturday's Calendar about the distribution of 
year-end films mistakenly reported that "Tom & Viv" had been pulled from 
release in New York after a two-week run. The film has been playing 
continuously there since its Dec. 2 opening. 
